{"tid":526254,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[鄭若驊僭建］想用虐兒，曾志偉強姦，東鐵線全死黎轉移視線？","createTime":"2018-01-11T12:49:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-11T13:36:24.000Z","uid":8000,"like":3,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"ce402802d104d1dcffd566c3e51cd7ec79cfcbc2","tid":526254,"uid":8000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-11T12:49:10.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">蘋果一爆你講大話 藍潔英就出聲？廿年唔出聲依家先話曾志偉？見單野爆唔起就整單東鐵死HQserver出黎 咁耐以黎都唔會咁 咁岩爆你單野出黎就死？</span><br />\n<br />\n我實追擊你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過《蘋果日報》今天頭條報道，翻查鄭若驊2008年購入單位時簽訂的按揭文件及樓契，發現當中載有物業的詳細描述，列明大屋「由地下、一樓、二樓及天台以及花園和車位組成」，當中並無提及有任何地庫；文件並引用第一手買家在1993年買入獨立屋時的合約圖則，顯示屋宇的組成部份，該圖亦顯示只有地下、一樓、二樓和天台，並無任何地庫。而兩份文件均由鄭若驊本人親自簽署。蘋果引述立法會議員涂謹申和陳淑莊認為，文件足證鄭早知物業原狀，並在買賣時已知悉地庫是僭建。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n想我唔追？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/kangourn\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fkangourn&d=hnFfUxQz5t0uSK50yrR20P%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=b03a9f85\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/kangourn</a>"},{"pid":"0d329e05adb7d1eaf4eee4c93c38b6cb3e8c2e83","tid":526254,"uid":35815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-11T12:51:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d6811c61a74f19832031e8c4a5faf6c6410dc765","tid":526254,"uid":24160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-11T12:52:55.000Z","msg":"重要有巨額六合彩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d32611534188ca8c148dd4fee8d28afa25c769e5","tid":526254,"uid":24160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-11T12:53:27.000Z","msg":"連登仔唔係好鍾意驅風嘅咩?<br />\nJ 啦<br />\n<img src=\"http://the-sun.on.cc/channels/news/20090228/img/sn05022803.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbn